data.transforming-libraries-in-node_modules#T:
By default, the Bun plugin skips transforming files from node_modules for performance.To transform a specific library, enable transformLibraries and narrow include/exclude:
wyw({
  transformLibraries: true,
  include: [/node_modules\\/(?:@fluentui)\\//],
});

data.disabling-vendor-prefixing#Disabling ven:
