data.additional-oxc-transformations#Additiona:
esbuild doesn't support chaining multiple onLoad transforms for the same file. If your project needs extra Oxc transforms
to run on the original TS/JSX source before WyW evaluation, enable oxcTransform:
wyw({
  oxcTransform: true,
  oxcOptions: {
    transform: {
      define: {
        __DEV__: 'false',
      },
    },
  },
});
Order: Oxc(source) → esbuild.transform() → WyW transform.This is opt-in and may impact performance, so keep filter narrow when possible.

